description: Chapter 1: Live animals
rule_of_origin: All animals of Chapter 1 are wholly obtained.

description: Chapter 2: Meat and edible meat offal
rule_of_origin: Production in which all the materials of Chapters 1 and 2 used are wholly obtained.

description: Chapter 3: Fish and crustaceans, molluscs and other aquatic invertebrates
rule_of_origin: Production in which all the materials of Chapter 3 used are wholly obtained.

description: Chapter 4: Dairy produce; birds'eggs; natural honey; edible products of animal origin, not elsewhere specified or included
rule_of_origin:
Production in which:
all the materials of Chapter 4 used are wholly obtained _and_
the total weight of non-originating materials of headings 17.01 and 17.02 does not exceed 20% of the weight of the product.

description: Chapter 5: Products of animal origin, not elsewhere specified or included
rule_of_origin: Production from non-originating materials of any heading.

description: Chapter 6: Live trees and other plants; bulbs, roots and the like; cut flowers and ornamental foliage
rule_of_origin: Production in which all the materials of Chapter 6 used are wholly obtained.

description: Chapter 7: Edible vegetables and certain roots and tubers
rule_of_origin: Production in which all the materials of Chapter 7 used are wholly obtained.

description: Chapter 8: Edible fruit and nuts; peel of citrus fruit or melons
rule_of_origin:
Production in which:
all the materials of Chapter 8 used are wholly obtained _and_
the total weight of non-originating materials of headings 17.01 and 17.02 does not exceed 20% of the weight of the product.

description: Chapter 9: Coffee, tea, maté and spices
rule_of_origin: Production from non-originating materials of any heading.

description: Chapter 10: Cereals
rule_of_origin: Production in which all the materials of Chapter 10 used are wholly obtained.

description: Chapter 11: Products of the milling industry; malt; starches; inulin; wheat gluten
rule_of_origin: Production in which all materials of Chapters 10 and 11, headings 07.01, 07.14, 23.02 to 23.03 or subheading 0710.10 used are wholly obtained.

description: Chapter 12: Oil seeds and oleaginous fruits; miscellaneous grains, seeds and fruit; industrial or medicinal plants; straw and fodder
rule_of_origin: CTH

description: Chapter 13: Lac; gums, resins and other vegetable saps and extracts
rule_of_origin: Production from non-originating materials of any heading in which the total weight of non-originating materials of headings 17.01 and 17.02 does not exceed 20% of the weight of the product.

description: Chapter 14: Vegetable plaiting materials; vegetable products not elsewhere specified or included
rule_of_origin: Production from non-originating materials of any heading.
